Scattershot/Nemesis Enforcer/Ares:



Scattershot stormed out of the Alliance base, the boosters in his feet 
activating, lifting him off into the air.  He took out his automatic rifle, 
firing down 25 explosive shells at Koj.  "DIE!  DIE! DIE!"

---

Nemesis Enforcer spread his leathery looking wings out, lifting off into the 
air, bringing his rapid-firing laser rifle into subspace.

---

Ares transformed to his tank mode, looking for a suitable enemy outside of 
the Alliance Base.
